text: Hornostaivka () may refer to several inhabited places in Ukraine: * Hornostaivka, administrative centre of Hornostaivka Raion, Kherson Oblast * Hornostaivka, Lenine Raion, a village in Lenine Raion, Crimea * Hornostaivka, Novotroitske Raion, a village in Novotroitske Raion, Kherson Oblast * Hornostaivka, Ripky Raion, a village in Ripky Raion, Chernihiv Oblast
title: Hornostaivka
